```

The assertion that catches "fill AND successful cancel of same order": in `case 1`, `cancelErr != ErrNotFound && cancelErr != ErrAlreadyFilled` evaluates to `true` when `cancelErr == nil`, so the test Fatalf's. A double fill (len==2) falls into `default` and Fatalf's immediately. A partial fill (qty < 10) in `case 1` is rejected by the `fills[0].Quantity != 10` check. **Pass.**

